data.title: Orthopedic, Sports Medicine and Spine Physicians
data.meta_description: Our orthopaedic doctors are experts in adult and pediatric orthopaedics care from neck to toe. Schedule with Chicago's top orthopaedic surgeons for bone, joint, spine and sports medicine care.
data.text:
We have your back.

At Duly Health and Care, we are here for you. Our team understands that bone, joint, and spine injuries have a physical and mental impact, and that recovery takes time.

We will partner with you on your health and care journey, and meet you wherever you are, to develop a specific treatment plan for your unique needs. Our tight-knit team of specialists will make sure you have the most complete medical, rehabilitative, diagnostic and surgical methods possible. Our goal is for you to reach your extraordinary health potentialbecause at Duly Health and Care, we believe that healthier makes happier.

Bone Health Clinic

If you are 50 and older, and have experienced a fragility fracture, we may refer you to the Duly Health and Care Bone Health Clinic, formerly known as Fracture Liaison Service. Learn more about managing your risk for future fractures here.

Workers Compensation

If you have a recently suffered a work-related injury, we can provide treatment options for your Workers Compensation claim or provide an Independent Medical Evaluation here.
